content: borisudovicic: Focused on project planning and defining key initiatives within the elizaos/eliza repository. They created 7 issues to outline significant upcoming work, including an "Eigencloud POC" (#5768), a "Cloud API Plugin for Framework LLMs" (#6049), and an effort to "Standardize Logging Across Core, CLI, and Server" (#6073). This activity indicates a focus on defining future work around cloud integration and core architecture.
